<section class="services" id="services">
  <div class="services__container">
    <h2 class="section-title">服务</h2>
    <div class="services__grid">
      <div class="service-card">
        <div class="service-card__number">01</div>
        <h3>网站与应用开发</h3>
        <p>运用最新技术，构建性能优异、可扩展的 Web 应用程序。</p>
      </div>
      <div class="service-card">
        <div class="service-card__number">02</div>
        <h3>移动应用开发</h3>
        <p>无论原生还是跨平台，为各种设备提供无缝体验的移动解决方案。</p>
      </div>
      <div class="service-card">
        <div class="service-card__number">03</div>
        <h3>UI/UX 设计</h3>
        <p>兼具美感和功能性的以用户为中心的设计，最大化品牌价值。</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <a href="/services/" class="services__link">查看全部服务</a>
  </div>
</section>

<style lang="scss">
  .services {
    padding: 3rem 1.5rem;
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;

    @media (min-width: 768px) {
      padding: 5rem 2rem;
    }

    &__grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 1.5rem;
      margin: 2rem 0;

      @media (min-width: 640px) {
        grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
      }

      @media (min-width: 1024px) {
        grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
        gap: 2rem;
        margin: 3rem 0;
      }
    }
    &__link {
      display: block;
      text-align: center;
      color: var(--c-primary);
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 600;
      margin-top: 1.5rem;
      transition: color 0.3s;

      @media (min-width: 768px) {
        margin-top: 2rem;
      }

      &:hover {
        color: var(--c-primary-light);
      }
    }
  }

  .service-card {
    padding: 1.5rem;
    background: var(--c-bg-secondary);
    border-radius: 8px;
    transition:
      transform 0.3s,
      box-shadow 0.3s;

    @media (min-width: 768px) {
      padding: 2rem;
    }

    &:hover {
      transform: translateY(-5px);
      box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }

    &__number {
      //   font-size: 2rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      //   color: var(--c-primary);
      margin-bottom: 1rem;

      @media (min-width: 768px) {
        // font-size: 2.5rem;
      }
    }

    h3 {
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      margin: 0 0 1rem 0;
      color: var(--c-text);

      @media (min-width: 768px) {
        font-size: 1.3rem;
      }
    }

    p {
      margin: 0;
      color: var(--c-text-sub);
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      line-height: 1.6;

      @media (min-width: 768px) {
        font-size: 0.95rem;
      }
    }
  }
</style>
